name: downloader
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool mp3_downloader.
Tool description: Search mp3 files by track, artist, album.
API description: This function searches for MP3 music using the given keywords and returns the results from the specified page.

keywords.description: The search keywords for finding MP3 music.

page.description: The page number of the search results to retrieve. Defaults to '1'.
